name: Steve Kazoleas
about: As a New York native with experience in multifamily property management and corporate real estate, I became a licensed Realtor in 2001. Education has always been key to my success—earning my Broker’s licenses in NY & NJ, CPM certification, and Assistant Bank Appraiser license. I continually pursue advanced courses through the National Association of REALTORS® to stay ahead in a dynamic market. My focus is helping sellers prepare their homes for top-dollar sales while assisting buyers in finding the perfect place to call home.

reviews.review: I had a great experience working with Steve. He sold my house in Staten Island and helped us purchase a condo in New Jersey. Throughout both transactions, Steve demonstrated honesty and trustworthiness, always putting our best interests first. I truly felt that he cared about his clients and wanted to ensure we made the right decisions. He's a kind and genuine person, and I would wholeheartedly recommend him to anyone looking for a dedicated and caring Realtor!
Very personable, knowledgeable, and easy to talk to
Knowledgeable, communicative and supportive.

Steve was amazing! He was honest, kind & decent. Steve always made himself available to answer our questions. He was always willing to go the extra mile to get our home sold. I would definitely recommend Steve he has definitely become our Realtor for Life!!!

Steve was an excellent realtor. We are very lucky to have worked with him. He was accessible at all times, and made this difficult process simple. We highly recommend working with Steve to find your dream home!!!

name: Akeem Smith
about:
Meet Akeem, an accomplished and highly motivated real estate agent with a passion for helping clients achieve their real estate goals. Known for his unparalleled responsiveness, persistence, and consistency, Akeem works tirelessly to ensure his clients' needs are met and exceeded.

Akeem has built an extensive network of professionals throughout his career, including lenders, lawyers, contractors, home inspectors, and licensed appraisers. He firmly believes that having the right people around him is key to delivering exceptional service and making the buying and selling process as stress-free as possible for his clients.

As a natural problem solver, Akeem is committed to providing his clients with the best solutions to any challenges that may arise during the real estate process. He consistently adds value to his clients' experiences and is dedicated to delivering top-notch service at all times.

As Albert Einstein once said, "Strive not to be of success, but rather to be of value," and this quote is one that Akeem lives by. Driven by the belief that true success is achieved by providing value, Akeem consistently strives to provide superior value to his clients and ensure their complete satisfaction with their real estate experience.

Whether you are a first-time buyer, a seller looking to get the best price for your home, or a landlord looking to rent out your property, Akeem has the expertise and knowledge to help you make the best decisions for your real estate journey. With his unwavering dedication, passion, and exceptional service, Akeem is the agent you can trust to guide you through the process with confidence and ease.

name: Anjely BisaiAnjely Bisai
about: Anjely is an experienced real estate agent who has gained a lot of skills and necessary knowledge in this field. She has been in the real estate business since 2006 but ventured into the mortgage business industry as far back as 1996. Her wealth of knowledge also extends to this industry, as she knows and understands every aspect of it. While dealing with her clients, she makes sure to communicate with them well with the end result being to understand exactly what they want. Coupled with an unparalleled customer service, ability to pay attention to details, decision-making skills, extensive knowledge on the necessary steps to take to get the best deals and huge dedication, she strives to meet your objectives, goals and challenge. She won’t be satisfied until the job is done!

name: David Tom
about: I’ve been a real estate agent in my hometown of New York since 1999. Studying real estate, it turns out, wasn't just about the property. It was about culture, history, geography and art. I’ve always been fascinated by stories about owning and renting homes in the city. My story began with luxury condos overlooking Central Park that inspired me to become an agent building my business to $20 million in sales over 3 years and closing over 50 deals. I pride myself on listening to client needs and known for being accessible to clients is what motivates me to find their dream home. Clients choose to work with me because of my knowledge, the expertise and experience to successfully close the deal. I love that working at Redfin gives me the opportunity to focus on each client and save them money.

reviews.review: David is very knowledgeable, always responsive and personable. I felt supported throughout my home purchase.

David was extremely helpful and kind from beginning to end of the process. David was always quickly responsive and willing to go the extra mile. I am very grateful to have worked with this on my home purchase.

name: Samantha Conca
about: My main goal is customer service, and always being available to my clients. There will never be a time that I don't respond to you within 5 minutes, I don't do this part time or full time, I work ALL the time!!!! I really love people and it's about finding exactly what they are looking for that becomes my mission.

reviews.review: Thank you so much Samantha, for your patience and expertise throughout this stressful process. Even with me being in an entirely different state, you stood by my side and guided me every step of the way. I couldn’t be more grateful for your dedication and all you did to ensure this sale was a success. May God bless you abundantly and continue to fuel the passion that drives you. I truly appreciate everything. With heartfelt thanks, Chanel
Samantha is a diligent, conscientious and zealous realtor who advocates for her clients. I would definitely recommend her to others seeking to buy or sell their home.

Throughout our home-buying process, Samantha was incredibly communicative. She promptly answered calls and emails, keeping us informed about every development. Her ability to clearly explain complex contract details was particularly helpful. We were also impressed by Samantha's negotiation skills. She managed to lower the asking price significantly, saving us thousands. Her strategy during the negotiation phase was impressive, as she leveraged her market knowledge to our advantage. Finally, I have to describe Samantha in one word I will just say that she CARES.

I would definitely recommend Samantha. Samantha followed through on everything from the very beginning to the very end. She made the buying process less stressful because she completely understood what I was looking for and communicated with me every step of the way. I have already referred her to two friends and will continue to do so.

Samantha had our best interests when selling our home and purchasing our new home. I was happy with the price I sold for and the price I purchased for. She works hard and actively listened to our needs. Hands down there is no other realtor I would use!

name: Gina Conzo
about:
When working with clients to find them the perfect home, Gina Conzo serves as a trusted advisor and true market expert as she walks them through the home buying process from A-Z. Specializing in the downtown luxury market, Gina's professionalism paired with her industry expertise are essential components in ensuring her clients find the perfect home.

Gina loves cultivating and nurturing relationships, and real estate allows her to do so all the while exploring her favorite city and supporting people as they find their new home or investment property. She has a strong business acumen and believes in keeping the values of honesty, integrity, and accountability at the forefront of each deal while going above and beyond for her clients.

Prior to her career in real estate, Gina worked for over a decade with some of the most prestigious luxury brands worldwide including Oscar De La Renta, Stella McCartney, and Brunello Cucinelli, which helped build her international client base. In her spare time, Gina enjoys seeking out new restaurants, loves to travel, practices yoga, pilates, and meditation regularly.

reviews.review: Gina is simply the best! She is ridiculously quick to respond, listened well to what we needed, and was flexible in meeting our needs. She is personable, yet tough. Gina was clear in what we needed to do and transparent throughout the entire 8 month process. She was outstanding!

property_info.address: 136 E 36th St Unit 2c, New York, NY

reviews.review: I had an enjoyable experience buying a co-op apartment with assistance from Gina. From the initial contact through the board's application and finally the closing period, Gina has been tremendously helpful. I would not be able to purchase this apartment without her assistance. Thank you!!

Gina is absolutely the best. This was not my first home purchase, and I have worked with other agents before, but Gina is better than everyone I have worked with. She is always there for you, from start to closing, taking complete ownership of the entire process. She also helped me finding my legal representation, insurance, home inspection etc. I will strongly recommend Gina, if you are looking for a real estate agent. She is not only good at her job, but also a really awesome person to work with.

My wife and I met Gina via a cold call. She offered her services after we had asked to see a listing on the Redfin website. She was so nice, knowledgeable and not pushy which is exactly what we were looking for. Gina moved fast and showed us several listings, helped us find a great home and was there with us for every step of the process. We are so happy we chose her as our agent.

Gina was amazing from the get go. She took the time to understand what I was looking for and was tireless in helping me find the right place. She was always available for any questions regardless of day or time and is a wealth of knowledge on the market. I really appreciated her honesty throughout the process, and she helped guide me through every step of my first home purchase. I would highly recommend Gina to everyone, as she is fantastic to work with.

name: Akeem Smith
about:
Meet Akeem, an accomplished and highly motivated real estate agent with a passion for helping clients achieve their real estate goals. Known for his unparalleled responsiveness, persistence, and consistency, Akeem works tirelessly to ensure his clients' needs are met and exceeded.

Akeem has built an extensive network of professionals throughout his career, including lenders, lawyers, contractors, home inspectors, and licensed appraisers. He firmly believes that having the right people around him is key to delivering exceptional service and making the buying and selling process as stress-free as possible for his clients.

As a natural problem solver, Akeem is committed to providing his clients with the best solutions to any challenges that may arise during the real estate process. He consistently adds value to his clients' experiences and is dedicated to delivering top-notch service at all times.

As Albert Einstein once said, "Strive not to be of success, but rather to be of value," and this quote is one that Akeem lives by. Driven by the belief that true success is achieved by providing value, Akeem consistently strives to provide superior value to his clients and ensure their complete satisfaction with their real estate experience.

Whether you are a first-time buyer, a seller looking to get the best price for your home, or a landlord looking to rent out your property, Akeem has the expertise and knowledge to help you make the best decisions for your real estate journey. With his unwavering dedication, passion, and exceptional service, Akeem is the agent you can trust to guide you through the process with confidence and ease.

Treats clients with the utmost respect and transparency, always looking out for their best interests. Not just looking to make a quick sale. However, works with a strong sense of urgency. Understands that the majority of the transaction process is a people process that requires relationship development. Is known as the nice one with a strong sense for business deals.

reviews.review: Devi was very helpful and always within reach.

I had a nice experience working with Devi for finding my home, thanks to her I have found a home for my family, Her willingness for taking her time with me for looking houses is extraordinary, very professional and client oriented. Devi was always available when I needed her assistance and information during purchase process of my home.
Exceptional!!

reviews.review: Ms Devi is an exceptional person with beautiful personality, extremely patient , and very devoted to her clients, her main goal is to not only make her clients happy but to also help them reach their goals

Devi yee is the best! She was thorough and professional and great to work with. She kept us apprised about available appointments and always let us know as soon as a new house came on the market. She was honest and forthright- no games. After dealing with several other brokers in the queens area and being disappointed, we felt lucky to find devi is absolutely wonderful to work with. It’s like having a friend on the “inside” that is working for you. She really care about hers clients as well as the community and neighborhood she live in. She is like family now. Thank you devi

name: David Tom
about: I’ve been a real estate agent in my hometown of New York since 1999. Studying real estate, it turns out, wasn't just about the property. It was about culture, history, geography and art. I’ve always been fascinated by stories about owning and renting homes in the city. My story began with luxury condos overlooking Central Park that inspired me to become an agent building my business to $20 million in sales over 3 years and closing over 50 deals. I pride myself on listening to client needs and known for being accessible to clients is what motivates me to find their dream home. Clients choose to work with me because of my knowledge, the expertise and experience to successfully close the deal. I love that working at Redfin gives me the opportunity to focus on each client and save them money.

reviews.review: David is very knowledgeable, always responsive and personable. I felt supported throughout my home purchase.

reviews.review: He was at utmost professional, knowledgeable and have so much patience. I will definitely recommend him to friends and family. Being a first time buyer he made the whole process so smooth. Thank you!

David was a fantastic, trusted advisor to us throughout the whole home buying journey! As out of state buyers, his intricate knowledge of the NYC market was invaluable. His recommendations helped us find the perfect home and ensured a smooth closing. Highly recommended!

reviews.review: David is an excellent realtor who takes the time to explain the many details and nuances of the New York market. He'll fight hard for what you want and dispense guidance when needed. I would not hesitate to recommend David and will work with him again.

David was extremely helpful and kind from beginning to end of the process. David was always quickly responsive and willing to go the extra mile. I am very grateful to have worked with this on my home purchase.
